1LT Overton;

Here are some documents which will need to be added to the 'planning
portal.'

I'd like to do an Orders Consistency Review and construct a 'Orders
Brief-back' (Summary) of the expectations for 3 RGT, if that is possible.

I did reach out to the BN CDRs in re your comments about 'the gouge'
getting down to the lowest level. I will keep an eye on this issue as it is
important. I hope it isn't something that has 'popped up' due to the
"Ferguson Effect (FE)."

And, I will be forwarding a message from COL Roark to me which originated
from CSM John Barton, 1 RGT for inclusion into the OIC Notes and
documentation.

I'm currently answering COL Roark's email question in re CSM Barton's
message right now. I will then read over the DIV OPORD. I am available by
phone / text / email should you have any questions.

-- 
V/R

JOHN T. SHEAF
LTC, TNSG
S3, 3 RGT
717.673.6177
john.sheaf@tnstateguard.org

